waitToLoad

public void waitToLoad()
Used to wait a certain period for form to be loaded. If the user action will not generate any http request, please do not use this api, such as clicking a text field. However, tree and menu expansion, finder search will still need pause, since these are data retrieving action and this api can not handle these cases.
